Package: libsndifsdl2-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Provides localization data for libsndifsdl2.
 This package is required by all packages which are utilizing libsndifsdl2.

Package: libsndifsdl2-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libsndifsdl2-common,
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: SDL2-based sound support for the fizmo interpreter.
 This library provides sound functionality related to the fizmo interpreter.

